featured_question.question: Which is time pray for Thursday???
featured_question.answer: What you mean which time pray for Thursday.. we have to pray 5 times a day.. 1.Fajr (around 30 mins before Sunrise),  2. Zohar (anytime after 12:30 to 2:30.. in mosques usually at 1:15), 3. Asar (anytime from 4:45 to 5:30), 4. Magrib ( immediately after sunset so time varies for summer and winters), 5. Isha after usually 8 PM.. apart from that Juma(Friday) prayer at 1 to 2pm in most of the mosques.
